            "title": "港股曾跌208點   比亞迪曾失百元關",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股恒生指數低開後跌幅擴大，暫最低見26073，跌209點或0.8%，現報26080點，跌202點或0.77%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數跌101 點或1.69%，報5949點  ; 恒生國企指數報9248，跌97點或1.05%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"比亞迪(資料圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250902_FI_01211_BP_1200.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"比亞迪(資料圖片)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250902_FI_01211_BP_1200.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">比亞迪(資料圖片)</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大市成交1245.41億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">信義光能(00968)跌4.51%報3.6元 ; 中芯(00981)跌4.74%，報75.45元 ; 比亞迪(01211)跌3.84%，報100.2元，最低見97.5元，趺6.43%，為表現最差三藍籌股。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">藥業股跑贏，翰森製藥(03692)升2.69%，報35.12元 ; 中生製藥(01177)升2.62%，報7.05元 ; 友邦(01299)升2.53%，報75.05元，升幅藍籌股中居首三位。石藥(01093)升2.14%，報7.63元。</p>\n</div>",
